title: Tiffany & Co.
description: Tiffany & Co.'s brand colors include the iconic 'Tiffany Blue' represented by the specific shade of blue (0097A3). This is complemented by a bright aqua color (5CDFE5), a classic white (FFFFFF), a muted silver gray (A19E9E), and a dark charcoal gray (636363). These colors are found in the brand's various marketing materials and are showcased in their official brand book available online.
